But were you able to manage the Overflows !?

**Hint for recursion :**
* start building the very first number from string and check if it is possible to complete the sequence , (make previous number from remaining string)
* isPossible function takes few parameters ( string s, currIndex i, targetNumber)
* if index has reached the end then return true as we have finished the string successfully
* if we have made the number then call for recursion again from next index and targetNumber-1

