Initially, I was thinking of BFS. However, after looking at the first hint, I used what I learned from the Next Permutation problem to create the kth smallest wonderful number. Then, I compared the digits to the original number and if there was a mismatch, I initiated necessary the swaps and tallied up the total count of swaps.


